    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Load the movie IDs and titles**\n",
        "\n",
        "The u.item file contains information about the movies in the MovieLens dataset. Our group only needs to use the movie identification number and movie for this part of the project."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "B4ywwtuqKY6l"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# load only the item ID and movie title columns\n",
        "movies = pd.read_csv(\n",
        "    \"/content/ml-100k/u.item\",\n",
        "    sep=\"|\",\n",
        "    names=[\"item_id\", \"title\"],\n",
        "    usecols=[0, 1],\n",
        "    encoding=\"latin-1\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# show the first five movies\n",
