    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Examine the dataset**\n",
        "\n",
        "The two tables are inspected before cleaning.\n",
        "\n",
        "The ratings table contains the user–movie interactions, including the user ID, item ID, rating, and timestamp.\n",
        "\n",
        "The movie table contains the item ID and corresponding movie title."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "m8F-q-ddKwq1"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# show the number of rows and columns in the ratings table\n",
        "print(\"Ratings dataset dimensions:\", ratings.shape)\n",
        "\n",
        "# display the first five rating records\n",
        "display(ratings.head())\n",
        "\n",
        "# show ratings column names, data types, and nonmissing counts\n",
        "ratings.info()\n",
        "\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 414
        },
        "id": "1xmRCphgKuQG",
        "outputId": "b9349395-0b52-4662-a4f4-309dc872fd5d"
      },
