    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Check the data types and rating values**\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "The project instructions state that:\n",
        "\n",
        "User IDs should be integers.\n",
        "Item IDs should be integers.\n",
        "Ratings should be floats."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "rDVCaaBBfDu2"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# print a heading for the ratings data types\n",
        "print(\"Ratings data types:\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# show the type assigned to each ratings column\n",
        "print(ratings.dtypes)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# print a heading for the movie data types\n",
        "print(\"\\nMovie data types:\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# show the type assigned to each movie column\n",
        "print(movies.dtypes)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "acu5xKyVQg7m",
        "outputId": "39c282ec-285c-40c2-d751-413b4b9ba5e9"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
